Dear Anne:<br><br>
&quot;Less conditional&quot; means not trying to control.<br><br>
Funny thing...when you are filled with fear of being hurt or losing something important..you automatically start controlling.<br><br>
Trust seems to be the opposite of control..actually it means giving control to others..I believe in you...I have faith in you..I share your values..So, I gonna let you drive!<br><br>
Kinda hard to do when you just survived a hell of a carwreck!....Vietnam..divorce..loss of job..etc.<br><br>
Combat veterans don't have a patent on PTSD.<br><br>
I love you more that Paul does...Honest Mom!<br><br>
MTF
